{"tid":1968530,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"# 每人追擊梁耀忠","createTime":"2020-04-11T17:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T17:39:16.000Z","uid":323538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5797792dca0daa9e0e59a437ad5ff42f178a38","tid":1968530,"uid":323538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"【追擊的宣言】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">梁耀忠最大問題係咩？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n永續社運？No！小編認為，若果一個人要永續社運，其實很可取。因為社會運動正正是推動社會改革。但梁不是，所以說他永續的是社運，那應該是對社運的恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他永續，是他的議席。他的事業。他的王國。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n梁最大問題是<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">僵化</span></strong></span>。梁只想永續自己最熟悉的部分，而對他人角度、觀點和關心的事不作思考，也不會反省。<br />\n<br />\n小編相信選民眼晴是雪亮。若一個人能虛心學習、反省自身、貼近民情、力求創新和突破的話，就算不是全體選民支持，也不會淪落到被人取笑。<br />\n<br />\n退一百萬步。若果他只是個普遍的老人家，或者他是你父母。他要永續自己的細藝，其實也問題不大。關注點只是有沒有錢、時間和空間。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但若果梁耀忠要永續他的僵化和議席，卻要全港市民陪他一個搞細藝。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你願意嗎？ 而我不願意，僅是如此。<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n這Post 只作每日紀錄用途、追擊資訊分享及為大家提供追擊用素材。<br />\n偶爾會 貼出 追擊任務，但追唔追擊就睇大家心情！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.me/fxxkoffleung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Ffxxkoffleung&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=37dc3d6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.me/fxxkoffleung</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n請大家呼籲身邊人 Unlike 梁耀忠專頁。<br />\n<br />\n4月12日圖片：<br />\n 唔洗驚！有01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKb7p1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKb7p1s.jpg&h=d4ddcdfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPMGus8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPMGus8.jpg&h=08cf62ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PsT2dUO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPsT2dUO.jpg&h=2a848cd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWXePs9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWXePs9.jpg&h=a2eb4bb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f8a4ee5b830ce90480dfdc22cb18ba7416fef72","tid":1968530,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"你好難去unlike佢page <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身都唔冇like"},{"pid":"bcd6b22a4b98861f700ecf89d4521c37db8a4dad","tid":1968530,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國家咁Q多新任務<br />\n家下係咪覺得人人都唔識佢"}]}